Class CompositeObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.CompositeObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective

    public class CompositeObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This objective collects a list of other objectives. It returns the weighted sum of the objectives.
